      "ResultSets": [
        {
          "Description": {
            "Id": "outcome_1_0",
            "Name": "Time out",
            "Details": "[[TGT_MW,{TGT_MW.Callsign}]] and [[SCN_MW,{SCN_MW.Callsign}]] immediately come to attention as you slowly walk over.\r\n\r\nYou stop in front of {TGT_MW.Callsign}, and {TGT_MW.SUBJ} carefully {TGT_MW.Gender?NonBinary:avoid|Default:avoids} your eyes, rigidly looking just past your shoulder.\r\n\r\n\"Pilot, <i>I</i> am the commanding officer on this ship. Not you. No one cares about your noble upbringing. You need to leave that thinking behind.\"\r\n\r\nGesturing to the room, \"You need these MechWarriors to have your back out there, or you are going to catch a stray AutoCannon round in the back.\" You give {SCN_MW.Callsign} a pointed look. \"â€¦Which had better not happen, understand? I don't need my 'Mechs getting damaged by my own employees.\"",
